  "subject": "Revert CCSDM CLM jobs to java 17 / maven 3.8",
  "commit_message": "Revert CCSDM CLM jobs to java 17 / maven 3.8\n\nCCSDK CLM jobs are failing when run with java 21 / maven 3.9.\nFor now, we can revert these jobs to Java 17 so we can verify\nthird party vulnerability fixes for Paris release, and then\nwe can work on finding a solution when we are ready\nto integrate our OpenDaylight Scandium changes.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-4096\nChange-Id: I8ec60ed1035bbe21a6e6200f0b80f36aec54a2b9\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\n",
